javax.security.identitystore.persistence

Interface JaasSubjectPrincipalResolver


  • public interface JaasSubjectPrincipalResolver
    JaasSubjectPrincipalResolver is used by JaasIdentityStore to determine caller principals from the JAAS Subject.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      String getCaller(Subject subject)
      Determine the caller name.
      List<String> getCallerGroups(Subject subject, String callerName)
      Determine the caller groups.
      List<String> getCallerRoles(Subject subject, String callerName)
      Determine the caller roles.

    • Method Detail

      • getCaller

        String getCaller(Subject subject)
        Determine the caller name.
        Parameters:
        subject - The authenticated JAAS subject.
        Returns:
        The caller name

      • getCallerGroups

        List<String> getCallerGroups(Subject subject,
                             String callerName)
        Determine the caller groups.
        Parameters:
        subject - The authenticated JAAS subject.
        callerName - The caller name
        Returns:
        The list of groups that the specified Caller is in, empty list if none, null if not supported.

      • getCallerRoles

        List<String> getCallerRoles(Subject subject,
                            String callerName)
        Determine the caller roles.
        Parameters:
        subject - The authenticated JAAS subject.
        callerName - The caller name
        Returns:
        The list of roles that the specified Caller has, empty list if none, null if not supported.
